4e86 C 31 D 5

A redox-regulated disulphide may form between two units of Defensin alpha 5 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Defensin alpha 5

5cuj F 30 F 31

Peptide name
Defensin alpha 5

5cui C 10 C 31

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Defensin alpha 5 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.

Peptide name
Defensin alpha 5

4rbw D 3 D 20

A redox-regulated disulphide may form within Defensin alpha 5 at these cysteines. However, the redox score of this cysteine pair is lower than any known redox-active disulphide.
